{"tid":383271,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[2018DSE] 自修英文既巴絲打入一入黎","createTime":"2017-09-01T10:44:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-20T16:56:24.000Z","uid":125535,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"02fbcaf83708e6d983cd794c3f38a58060ea2675","tid":383271,"uid":125535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T10:44:29.000Z","msg":"有好野介紹俾自修英文既巴打絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n小弟之前同唔少巴絲打幫過自修生<br />\n今年小弟邀請到一個係<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">中學教DSE班既英文老師</span></strong>攪個<span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文科自修講座</span></ins></strong></span>,希望幫到自修英文既朋友建立到有效溫書方法<br />\n<br />\n講座內容會有:<br />\n1. 回顧2017試卷<br />\n2. 重溫各卷技巧及得分關鍵<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">3. 自修生缺乏功課/測驗/考試既情況下，如何在7個月有效提升英文水平</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n個人覺得第三Part最重要。英文科做晒PP唔等於溫好英文，底子係好重要。底子要加厚就要搵到<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">合適既溫書方法</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n識得一個巴打一年內由<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>U升4</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。佢同大家一樣都好勤力溫英文，但因為佢有人指導左佢有效既方法正確，令佢過到關之餘升左咁多分。方法唔係咩神奇野，只係用岩方法不斷去<strong>睇、背、寫</strong>...... <br />\n<br />\n日期: 23/9/2017<br />\n時間: 2:30-4:30PM<br />\n地點: 太子<br />\n<br />\n誠邀位自修英文既巴絲打一齊黎聽下<br />\n英文科掌握到溫書方法同埋能夠堅持落去就會見到進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有興趣可以係下面條拎留低聯絡方法<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/2xGCDL\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2F2xGCDL&d=rMgaN5TqaeNk4%2FQu35GHkHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=3f9317b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/2xGCDL</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">利申: 唔係介紹私補, 冇私補介紹, 誓不牟利, 只係想幫自修生</span></span>"},{"pid":"28caa6ab3f2abca4ffefdd86eb8ec726cd0692b2","tid":383271,"uid":125535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T08:45:13.000Z","msg":"細力一推"},{"pid":"43098ada54b30106c8675f3175449aa6a0bf77d7","tid":383271,"uid":135735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T08:46:55.000Z","msg":"一定要自修先去得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d913796e297f27a8e3faa00a06e02fc4c14c1be2","tid":383271,"uid":125535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T10:01:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一定要自修先去得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係自修既人會想聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},{"pid":"dc724f22590bda388dd4f201fca92c90dc5b1602","tid":383271,"uid":8514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T10:09:25.000Z","msg":"幫幫我由1升3"},{"pid":"937f71a6bd7d754d0ab2e8603c06b89a9b6e1873","tid":383271,"uid":125535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T06:45:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幫幫我由1升3</blockquote><br />\n可以幫忙，不過最後要靠自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1351aea7f0636ceb340af14da7bc9ba7073acaa3","tid":383271,"uid":125535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T15:46:19.000Z","msg":"輕推"},{"pid":"2ccec8f4df38a278cf9a2c3ccfc9be2ec094af78","tid":383271,"uid":125535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T03:42:24.000Z","msg":"早晨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0128f2e4881199b21ea5038ee90e897af7ff7fac","tid":383271,"uid":125535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T11:10:58.000Z","msg":"輕推"},{"pid":"7ad78a9d6b9f937b87ea8c31c2f6e894eb597f75","tid":383271,"uid":11644,"like"